 speaker at research workshops and conferences worldwide he also serves on the board of supernova companies llc and has been appointed a trustee of credit suisse funds openend portfolios in addition dr guptas education which includes a phd in accounting from stanford university and his oversight of the financial management of the olin business school enhance his contribution to the board and in particular to the audit committee source caleres inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view mahendra r guptas full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like mahendra r gupta more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in mahendra r guptas network and community follow changes in mahendra r guptas employment and moneyinmotion connect with mahendra r gupta through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example mahendra r gupta mahendra r guptas connections  sign up now to view mahendra r guptas  connections » russell c hammer former senior vice president and chief financial officer caleres inc diane m sullivan chief executive officer president and chairman of the board caleres inc richard m ausick division president famous footwear caleres inc patricia g mcginnis board member caleres inc ward m klein board member caleres inc steven w korn board member caleres inc william p mcginnis board member caleres inc john w schmidt division president brand portfolio caleres inc carla c hendra board member caleres inc michael f neidorff chairman president and chief executive officer centene corporation popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla michael c montgomery board member nmi holdings inc × claim your profile coming soon interested in updat